*4. Abstract*  
The Robust Apartment Complex Operation Facilitator is a web-based DBMS application developed using Flask and MySQL. It digitizes day-to-day operations of a residential complex including flat management, resident registration, visitor logs, maintenance billing, and complaint tracking. The system provides an admin dashboard with real-time stats and CRUD operations for all modules. It reduces manual paperwork, improves transparency, and ensures efficient data management for apartment societies.

