Visitor Checkout	Click checkout	out_time updated	Pass
*14. Conclusion*  
The system successfully automates apartment operations and provides a reliable database-driven solution. It eliminates manual registers and gives instant access to occupancy, dues, and complaints data.

*15. Future Scope*  
1. Login system for admin vs security guard roles
2. Email/SMS alerts for due bills
3. Mobile app for residents to raise complaints
4. Payment gateway integration
5. Export reports to PDF/Excel

